uter business. *[[Zenith Data Systems]] - Merged With [[Packard Bell]] and [[NEC]] in 1996 *[[Zeos]] - merged into [[MPC Corporation]] in 1996, which in turn filed for Chapter 11 bankruptcy in 2008.
