{{GeoGroup|article=Operation Tinderbox}}

'''Operation Tinderbox'''<ref name=LT_1 /> was a series of 14 [[nuclear test]]s conducted by the United States in 1979-1980 at the [[Nevada Test Site]]. These tests followed the ''[[Operation Quicksilver (1978)|Operation Quicksilver]]'' series and preceded the ''[[Operation Guardian]]'' series.

{{see also|List of nuclear weapons tests of the United States}}

